author: stsp
msg: Fix issue #3698 "svn patch should validate svn: properties".
(close_target_streams): Fix weird indentation issues. Do not close the
reject stream, because it is now needed beyond this point.
(write_out_rejected_hunks): Close the reject stream here, right before
the reject files are copied into the working copy.
(install_patched_prop_targets): If setting a property fails because it
is invalid (e.g. it does not apply to the node kind, like svn:executable
set on a directory), then reject all hunks associated with the property.
This also requires some changes in the way this function handles dry-run.
(patch_dir_properties): Fix expectations of this test. Together with the
above changes, this makes the test pass.
